er routes to your application and deploy many hosting platform with a zero-config experience.",[595,612,613],{"v-slot:links":5},[614,615],"app-hero-links",{},[617,618],"hero-features",{":features":619},"[{\"title\":\"Fast\",\"description\":\"Enjoy the fast Vite 8 (rolldown powered) development experience with HMR on the server and optimized for production.\",\"icon\":\"i-lucide-zap\",\"color\":\"text-amber-500\",\"bgColor\":\"bg-amber-500/10\",\"borderColor\":\"group-hover:border-amber-500/30\"},{\"title\":\"Agnostic\",\"description\":\"Deploy the same codebase to any deployment provider with zero config and locked-in.\",\"icon\":\"i-lucide-globe\",\"color\":\"text-sky-500\",\"bgColor\":\"bg-sky-500/10\",\"borderColor\":\"group-hover:border-sky-500/30\"},{\"title\":\"Minimal\",\"description\":\"Nitro adds no overhead to runtime. Build your servers with any modern tool you like.\",\"icon\":\"i-lucide-feather\",\"color\":\"text-emerald-500\",\"bgColor\":\"bg-emerald-500/10\",\"borderColor\":\"group-hover:border-emerald-500/30\"}]",[621,622],"performance-showcase",{":metrics":623},"[{\"label\":\"Bare metal perf\",\"value\":\"~Native\",\"unit\":\"RPS\",\"description\":\"Using compile router, and fast paths for request handling.\",\"icon\":\"i-lucide-gauge\",\"color\":\"text-emerald-500\",\"bgColor\":\"bg-emerald-500/10\",\"barWidth\":\"95%\",\"barColor\":\"bg-emerald-500\"},{\"label\":\"Minimum install Size\",\"value\":\"Tiny\",\"unit\":\"deps\",\"description\":\"Minimal dependencies. No bloated node_modules.\",\"icon\":\"i-lucide-package\",\"color\":\"text-sky-500\",\"bgColor\":\"bg-sky-500/10\",\"barWidth\":\"15%\",\"barColor\":\"bg-sky-500\"},{\"label\":\"Small and portable output\",\"value\":\"‹ 10\",\"unit\":\"kB\",\"description\":\"Standard server builds produce ultra-small output bundles.\",\"icon\":\"i-lucide-file-output\",\"color\":\"text-violet-500\",\"bgColor\":\"bg-violet-500/10\",\"barWidth\":\"10%\",\"barColor\":\"bg-violet-500\"},{\"label\":\"FAST builds\",\"value\":\"‹ 1\",\"unit\":\"sec\",\"description\":\"Cold production builds complete in seconds, not minutes.\",\"icon\":\"i-lucide-timer\",\"color\":\"text-amber-500\",\"bgColor\":\"bg-amber-500/10\",\"barWidth\":\"12%\",\"barColor\":\"bg-amber-500\"}]",[625,626,627],"landing-features",{},[595,628,629,644,658,672,686,700,713,727,741],{"v-slot:body":5},[630,631,634,639],"feature-card",{"headline":632,"link":24,"link-label":633},"Routing","Routing docs",[595,635,636],{"v-slot:title":5},[598,637,638],{},"File-system routing",[595,640,641],{"v-slot:description":5},[598,642,643],{},"Create server routes in the routes/ folder and they are automatically registered. Or bring your own framework — H3, Hono, Elysia, Express — via a server.ts entry.",[630,645,648,653],{"headline":646,"link":85,"link-label":647},"Versatile","Explore deploy targets",[595,649,650],{"v-slot:title":5},[598,651,652],{},"Deploy everywhere",[595,654,655],{"v-slot:description":5},[598,656,657],{},"The same codebase deploys to Node.js, Cloudflare Workers, Deno, Bun, AWS Lambda, Vercel, Netlify, and more — zero config, no vendor lock-in.",[630,659,662,667],{"headline":660,"link":69,"link-label":661},"Storage","Storage docs",[595,663,664],{"v-slot:title":5},[598,665,666],{},"Universal storage",[595,668,669],{"v-slot:description":5},[598,670,671],{},"Built-in key-value storage abstraction powered by unstorage. Works with filesystem, Redis, Cloudflare KV, and more — same API everywhere.",[630,673,676,681],{"headline":674,"link":64,"link-label":675},"Caching","Caching docs",[595,677,678],{"v-slot:title":5},[598,679,680],{},"Built-in caching",[595,682,683],{"v-slot:description":5},[598,684,685],{},"Cache route handlers and arbitrary functions with a simple API. Supports multiple storage backends and stale-while-revalidate patterns.",[630,687,690,695],{"headline":688,"link":59,"link-label":689},"Server Entry","Server entry docs",[595,691,692],{"v-slot:title":5},[598,693,694],{},"Web standard server",[595,696,697],{"v-slot:description":5},[598,698,699],{},"Go full Web standard and pick the library of your choice. Use H3, Hono, Elysia, Express, or the raw fetch API — Nitro handles the rest.",[630,701,703,708],{"headline":18,"link":19,"link-label":702},"Renderer docs",[595,704,705],{"v-slot:title":5},[598,706,707],{},"Universal renderer",[595,709,710],{"v-slot:description":5},[598,711,712],{},"Use any frontend framework as your renderer. Nitro provides the server layer while your framework handles the UI.",[630,714,717,722],{"headline":715,"link":49,"link-label":716},"Plugins","Plugins docs",[595,718,719],{"v-slot:title":5},[598,720,721],{},"Server plugins",[595,723,724],{"v-slot:description":5},[598,725,726],{},"Extend Nitro's runtime behavior with plugins. Hook into lifecycle events, register custom logic, and auto-load from the plugins/ directory.",[630,728,731,736],{"headline":729,"link":39,"link-label":730},"Database","Database docs",[595,732,733],{"v-slot:title":5},[598,734,735],{},"Built-in database",[595,737,738],{"v-slot:description":5},[598,739,740],{},"Lightweight SQL database layer powered by db0. Pre-configured with SQLite out of the box, with support for PostgreSQL, MySQL, and Cloudflare D1.",[630,742,745,750],{"headline":743,"link":29,"link-label":744},"Assets","Assets docs",[595,746,747],{"v-slot:title":5},[598,748,749],{},"Static & server assets",[595,751,752],{"v-slot:description":5},[598,753,754],{},"Serve public assets directly to clients or bundle server assets for programmatic access. Works seamlessly across all deployment targets.",[756,757],"page-sponsors",{},[759,760,761],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .so5gQ, html code.shiki .so5gQ{--shiki-light:#D73A49;--shiki-default:#F97583;--shiki-dark:#F97583}html pre.shiki code .slsVL, html code.shiki .slsVL{--shiki-light:#24292E;--shiki-default:#E1E4E8;--shiki-dark:#E1E4E8}html pre.shiki code .sfrk1, html code.shiki .sfrk1{--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-default:#9ECBFF;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF}html pre.shiki c